com.mockrunner.jdbc

Class BasicJDBCTestCaseAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • junit.framework.Assert
      • junit.framework.TestCase
        • com.mockrunner.jdbc.BasicJDBCTestCaseAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    junit.framework.Test
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BankTest, BasicJDBCTestCaseAdapterTest, BookstoreTest, OrderDBTest

    public abstract class BasicJDBCTestCaseAdapter
extends junit.framework.TestCase
    Delegator for JDBCTestModule. You can subclass this adapter or use JDBCTestModule directly (so your test case can use another base class). This basic adapter can be used if you don't need any other modules. It does not extend BaseTestCase. If you want to use several modules in conjunction, consider subclassing com.mockrunner.jdbc.JDBCTestCaseAdapter. This class is generated from the JDBCTestModule and should not be edited directly.
